decks.notes: This deck focuses on using the Paradoxical Outcome card to generate card advantage and mana acceleration by bouncing artifacts back to hand. It aims to quickly assemble a powerful board state and overwhelm the opponent with a fast and efficient combo. The addition of Lurrus of the Dream-Den as a companion allows for additional recursion and value generation from the graveyard. The deck includes powerful Vintage staples such as Black Lotus and Time Walk to further increase its explosiveness and staying power. Overall, the deck is designed to quickly execute its combo strategy and outpace the opponent.
